text: Diadelia obliquenigrovittata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Breuning in 1980.BioLib.cz - Diadelia obliquenigrovittata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Diadelia Category:Beetles described in 1980
